{
  "stem": "18778.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He heard that the ship that was ahead of us had difficulties about unloading the passengers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Cuban government was making noises about not allowing the people to get off the ship.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so he decided that perhaps there would be-- as a German officer in a German uniform, he might intimidate his passengers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so he decided to call a few of the men among the passengers together to form a committee as a liaison, in case there's going to be a problem.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This was a very-- a Renaissance man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The captain was really a Renaissance man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We learned much more about him when we had our 50th anniversary in Miami and his nephew came over to tell us about him.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was an artist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was a poet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was a writer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he was a very smart man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was small of stature, but he ran that ship with an iron hand.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he had told his crew that the people whom they were going to serve on this trip were supposed to be treated like any other passengers that usually go on this-- are passengers on that liner.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were Jews, but they were to be treated with respect, just like any other passengers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe it took us 10 days, 10 days to reach Havana.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We left-- perhaps a little longer, perhaps close to two weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have-- I have the exact figures.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somewhere short of two weeks to reach Havana.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I remember it was early in the morning as we saw land and came close to the port.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
